[SN]TITLE[SN]
Join BBC Radio Scotland's Big Debate in Fort William

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
BBC Radio Scotland's Big Debate with Gordon Brewer will be broadcast from Fort William later this month.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The discussion programme will be at the Duncansburgh Macintosh Church Hall on 19 June.
To apply for tickets to join the audience, email bigdebate@bbc.co.uk for details.
The audience needs to be seated at 11:30 on the day of the broadcast.
